Package gw.api.webservice.addressbook.contactapi

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ABContactAPISearchExecutorHelper
    ABContactAPISearchResultHelper
    ABContactAPISearchSpec
    Specifies search result control parameters.
    ABContactSearchExecutor
    ABContactSearchResult
    ABContactSearchSortColumn
    Represents a column to sort on as part of a search.
    ABContactSearchSpec
    This class has parameters related to paging and sorting in addition to the ContactManager specific parameters in ABContactSearchSpecWithoutPaging. This is used by non-UI code which has to control paging and sorting.
    ABContactSearchSpecWithoutPaging
    Specifies various parameters to control search. Doesn't not include parameters related to paging and sorting. Pebbles handles that stuff for the UI separately.
    ABContactSubtypeFilter
    Used to restrict contact search results to those contacts which match one of the subtypes in the list.
    ABContactTagMatcher
    Used to restrict contact search results to those contacts which have the specified set of tags.
